双正态总体的抽样分布有
1. $U=\frac{(\bar{X}-\bar{Y})-\left(\mu_1-\mu_2\right)}{\sqrt{\sigma_1^2 / n_1+\sigma_2^2 / n_2}} \sim N(0,1)$;
2. $F=\left(\frac{\sigma_2}{\sigma_1}\right)^2 \frac{S_1^2}{S_2^2} \sim F\left(n_1-1, n_2-1\right)$;
3. 当 $\sigma_1^2=\sigma_2^2=\sigma^2$ 时, $T=\frac{(\bar{X}-\bar{Y})-\left(\mu_1-\mu_2\right)}{S_w \sqrt{1 / n_1+1 / n_2}} \sim t\left(n_1+n_2-2\right)$, 其中 $S_w^2=\frac{n_1-1}{n_1+n_2-2} S_1^2+\frac{n_2-1}{n_1+n_2-2} S_2^2$.

questions.question:
设 $(X_1, \cdots, X_m)$ 和 $(Y_1, \cdots, Y_n)$ 分别取自两个相互独立的正态总体 $N(\mu_1, \sigma_1^2)$ 及 $N(\mu_2, \sigma_2^2)$, 则服从 $F(m-1, n-1)$ 的统计量是 (    ).
$$
\begin{aligned}
& \bar{X}=\frac{1}{m} \sum_{i=1}^m X_i, \quad \bar{Y}=\frac{1}{n} \sum_{i=1}^n Y_i, \quad S_1^2=\frac{1}{m-1} \sum_{i=1}^m(X_i-\bar{X})^2, \quad S_2^2=\frac{1}{n-1} \sum_{i=1}^n(Y_i-\bar{Y})^2, \\
& S_3^2=\frac{1}{m} \sum_{i=1}^m(X_i-\mu_1)^2, \quad S_4^2=\frac{1}{n} \sum_{i=1}^n(Y_i-\mu_2)^2, \quad S_w=\sqrt{\frac{(m-1) S_1^2+(n-1) S_2^2}{m+n-2}}
\end{aligned}
$$

